snippet.title: Floralgraphic Memory | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
"After decided to skip school today, Rose whisked himself away to another world full of whimsies and magic."

ChaseFOX's fifth game.

Floralgraphic Memory is a tiny fantasy pastel drama kinetic visual novel that tells a story of a teenager named Rose who whisked himself away to another world after decided to skip school today.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2570830/Floralgraphic_Memory/
